reviews.review_text: I recently visited the  fitness world (Georgia) gym and had the pleasure of encountering an outstanding desk person ( Ivana) who truly made my experience remarkable. From the moment I walked in, she greeted me with a warm and friendly smile, instantly making me feel welcome. her exceptional customer service skills was evident as she patiently answered all my questions and provided me with a thorough tour of the gym facilities. she took the time to understand my fitness goals and offered valuable insights on various workout routines and classes that would best suit my needs. What impressed me the most was their genuine enthusiasm for helping others. Furthermore, the desk person displayed excellent knowledge of the gyms amenities, classes, and membership options. She went above and beyond to ensure I had all the information I needed to make an informed decision about becoming a member. I can confidently say that this desk person is an asset to the gym and plays a significant role in creating a positive and motivating environment for all members. I highly recommend visiting the gym and experiencing their exceptional service firsthand. Mahsa

Best gym ever! Friendly staff with a great manager, feels like you re part of the most vibrant family! Annasthesia, makes sure all members having great time and makes your experience memorable and unique! she s fun, supportive and very caring! The gym is clean and all facility is new. You ll go to this gym once, you don t want to be anywhere else!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Ella, Thank you for your feedback! I am glad to hear that your experience at Fitness World Georgia is memorable! See you during your next workout! Thanks, Annastasija

reviews.review_text: This is the best gym I have ever been to!! I ve been in so many gyms throughout my life and this one is by FAR the cleanest, most organized, and motivating gym. The staff are the best part though, they are amazing!!! I love the general manager here, Annastasija. Huge shout out to her! I ve found my forever gym :)

reviews.review_text: Fitness World is a great gym with excellent staff and top-notch equipment. From the moment I walked in, I was impressed by the welcoming and helpful attitude of the staff. Fred, the manager, who was especially helpful as he assisted me in signing up for my membership and pairing me with the perfect fitness trainer. I then was introduced to Annastasija, who has been nothing but amazing to work with. She designed a workout plan that was tailored to my fitness goals and made me look better than I have in months. Her expertise and knowledge was par none the best I have received compared to my past trainers. One thing that stands out about this location is the cleanliness of the gym. The equipment is always in good condition and maintained properly, which is a rarity in most other gyms. I never have to worry about finding dirty machines or broken equipment, which can be frustrating in other places. Overall, I highly recommend this location to anyone looking for a gym that is near a skytrain and overall friendly staff and wanting to hit their fitness goals.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Phillip, This review made our day!
